== 票房 ==
美国首周末收获1740万美圆，名列第五位<ref>{{cite web | url=http://boxofficemojo.com/weekend/chart/?yr=2012&wknd=07 | title=Weekend Box Office: February 17-19, 2012 | work=[[Box_Office_Mojo|Box Office Mojo]] | publisher=[[Internet_Movie_Database|Internet Movie Database]] | accessdate=February 21, 2012 | archive-date=2013-10-19 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131019065421/http://boxofficemojo.com/weekend/chart/?yr=2012&wknd=07 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

